'''Salvation''' could refer to:
*[[Salvation (flagship)|''Salvation'']], an [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate]] used as a [[Flagship/Legends|flagship]] of the [[Alliance Fleet/Legends|Alliance Fleet]]
*[[Salvation (medical frigate)|''Salvation'']], an EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate used as a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] [[Hospital ship/Legends|medical frigate]]
*[[Arbra/Legends|Arbra]], a planet nicknamed Salvation by the Alliance to Restore the Republic
*The ''[[Indenture]]'', a [[Firespray-31-class patrol and attack craft/Legends|''Firespray''-class]] attack ship, sometimes traveled under the name ''Salvation''.
